      <odd id="aspace_da03b74df1de3589f688237e718d0572">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 24-E (YRG 24-E), Records of departments, offices, programs, and projects of the Yale School of Forestry.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_dffe7f6886f898641b8000dc02a0517a">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the School of Forestry and Environmental Studies, 1982.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
